Annotation gives you the semantics for CDS view :

types :
1) View Annotations - Placed in front of define view statement 
                     @AbapCatalog.sqlViewName:'ZCDS_SQL_VIEW_EXP1'
                     @EndUserText.label:'Description for the'


2)Element Annotations : These are for elements of select list of CDS- placed in front or after the element of cds view
                        @Semmatics.amount.currencyCode:'local_currency_key'
                        @Sematics.currencyCode:true
3)Parameter Annotations : These are for parameter of the cds .placed before or after parameter
                         @Environment.systemField:#SYSTEM_DATE

4)Extension Annotations : these are for CDS view extension. placed in front of 'extend view' statement
                         @AbapCatalog.sqlViewAppendName:'zcds_sql_ex2'

5) Function Annotations : used for cds table function . placed in front of 'define table function' statement
